Recently, our research at the Center for Sexual Promotion at Indiana University completed the largest nationally representative survey of the US population in nearly 20 years. Specifically, we surveyed women and men ages 14 to 94 about their sexual lives as part of the National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior.
